Manterror/Counter Punch/Double Punch/Injector/Bumblebee:



Manterror, Counter Punch, and Double Punch arrive on the scene, seeing all 
the fuss over Dark Mouse.  


Manterror fires three ion disks at Ursa Major.


Counter Punch fires three plasma blasts off at Ursa Major.

Double Punch fires two enrgy-signature seeking missiles off at Dark Mouse.  

Bumblebee slams into a tree trunk, firing three stinger missiles off at Urs a 
Major.

Injector fired two missiles off at Striker.
